# Locked shortlist — pheno-harness eval matrix, 2026-07-04

**Status:** LOCKED per user message of 2026-07-04. No new SKU will be added without explicit sign-off.

**Two distinct roles, two distinct registries:**

- **Cloud baselines (10 models)** — paid/managed, accessed via `forge-dev → omniroute-dev → OpenRouter`. Source-of-truth is the OpenRouter catalog (`/api/v1/models`) cross-referenced against the HuggingFace repository the publisher chose. Pricing is per OpenRouter at the time of the call; OR discounts are non-stable and must be re-checked per eval run.
- **Self-hosted (3 models)** — weights on the 3090 Ti, served via `pheno-serve-dev` (SGLang primary, vLLM secondary per `config/inference_runners.yaml`). Source-of-truth is the HF repo. No OpenRouter involvement.

---

